  "texts": [
    "Once transparency about the internal mechanisms is lacking, users struggle to trust and accept the decisions made by the system.",
    "Users often desire understandable explanations for recommended choices.",
    "Addressing the challenge of model interpretability and explainability requires research involving natural language processing, explainable AI, human-computer interaction, and recommendation systems.",
    "The development of techniques that unveil the inner workings of language models, facilitate the generation of meaningful and accurate interpretations, and enable robust evaluation methods is the main focus.",
    "By providing transparent and interpretable recommendations, users can establish trust, understand the reasoning behind the recommendations, and make informed decisions."
  ],
